    <span key="877cc484f6134066a0781dd6ebc748f8"><span offset-key="877cc484f6134066a0781dd6ebc748f8:0">An SSL Certificate to enable SSL protection</span></span>

## 

<span key="23a2b5bb97804b5c95370554a4c50a5a"><span offset-key="23a2b5bb97804b5c95370554a4c50a5a:0">The Product Domain</span></span>

<span key="4405652789ef411089c183087791dba4"><span offset-key="4405652789ef411089c183087791dba4:0">Each Product will have one and only one domain that will be used for all network traffic to all endpoints in all projects. Please refer to the </span></span><a href="https://docs.labs.lambdaschool.com/standards/" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="2fd31708907a4b98b074aaf290256114" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_257-70305_259-70306-237__"><span data-key="6a503398090b473c90fa123a17b1094d"><span data-offset-key="6a503398090b473c90fa123a17b1094d:0">Labs Engineering Standards</span></span></span></a><span key="5457dac499a44b10b468a4c70ff06f69"><span offset-key="5457dac499a44b10b468a4c70ff06f69:0"> for naming details.</span></span>

![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)

<span key="478ed1d5b05d43649ea6971bfb3cba9d"><span offset-key="478ed1d5b05d43649ea6971bfb3cba9d:0">The product Hosted Zone must be created </span>*before*<span offset-key="478ed1d5b05d43649ea6971bfb3cba9d:2"> you can register the product domain name. This is because the name servers in the hosted zone </span>*must*<span offset-key="478ed1d5b05d43649ea6971bfb3cba9d:4"> be listed in the domain registration.</span></span>

<span key="eb1928bd1d734113be1e137eeaa1aeee"><span offset-key="eb1928bd1d734113be1e137eeaa1aeee:0">If these don't match, DNS doesn't work.</span></span>

<span key="38e80202f626420f81faed4ec7bdb0a7"><span offset-key="38e80202f626420f81faed4ec7bdb0a7:0">However, domain registrations can always be updated by an engineering manager should they change for some reason.</span></span>

## 

<span key="8cbe16a696524c848acd204487c1a175"><span offset-key="8cbe16a696524c848acd204487c1a175:0">Product Hosted Zone</span></span>

<span key="e3ed19584e474c40991c5449bf639565"><span offset-key="e3ed19584e474c40991c5449bf639565:0">An </span></span><a href="https://docs.aws.amazon.com/Route53/latest/DeveloperGuide/hosted-zones-working-with.html" class="css-4rbku5 css-1dbjc4n r-1loqt21 r-1471scf r-1otgn73 r-1i6wzkk r-lrvibr"><span data-key="bca5f1d0f44d45ce809f73e500b06b20" data-rnw-int-class="nearest_257-70305_259-70306-237__"><span data-key="433c752afa6e4051a6ff1c5d032bffe9"><span data-offset-key="433c752afa6e4051a6ff1c5d032bffe9:0">AWS Hosted Zone</span></span></span></a><span key="a66567cbae674ff9ad03850e6a0582a0"><span offset-key="a66567cbae674ff9ad03850e6a0582a0:0"> is a DNS resource for controlling name resolution for a domain. Each AWS Product Account will have a hosted zone setup to handle name requests for the product domain.</span></span>

### 

<span key="8e1922120b004c0b9ec0b0cc2508e118"><span offset-key="8e1922120b004c0b9ec0b0cc2508e118:0">Setup Hosted Zone</span></span>

1.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">1.</span>
    <span key="c63fbf184e4d401a8a84790aba547e23"><span offset-key="c63fbf184e4d401a8a84790aba547e23:0">Navigate to the Route 53 service in the product account</span></span>

2.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">2.</span>
    <span key="98fd4fe2ba84459093bb4520f85b44e5"><span offset-key="98fd4fe2ba84459093bb4520f85b44e5:0">Click 'Hosted Zones' on the menu to see the list of hosted zones</span></span>

3.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">3.</span>
    <span key="2fe30f7c00004462ad5647464af32abf"><span offset-key="2fe30f7c00004462ad5647464af32abf:0">You should see </span>*one*<span offset-key="2fe30f7c00004462ad5647464af32abf:2"> hosted zone with a domain name matching your product domain name</span></span>

4.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">4.</span>
    <span key="7eda9a591f964b5db20b032bd53e4635"><span offset-key="7eda9a591f964b5db20b032bd53e4635:0">If not, you can click 'Create Hosted Zone'</span></span>

    1.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">1.</span>
        <span key="e199463754da447d973d4fb0cc8e04d3"><span offset-key="e199463754da447d973d4fb0cc8e04d3:0">The domain name is your product domain name</span></span>

    2.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">2.</span>
        <span key="d8a410cdaad947e6b2689995a0158f8e"><span offset-key="d8a410cdaad947e6b2689995a0158f8e:0">Public Hosted Zone</span></span>

    3.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">3.</span>
        <span key="36d5aeb4185948d8b9bb50ab7cd902f3"><span offset-key="36d5aeb4185948d8b9bb50ab7cd902f3:0">No tags required</span></span>

    4.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">4.</span>
        <span key="745e29bfbfad47aa9e2207692131726b"><span offset-key="745e29bfbfad47aa9e2207692131726b:0">Click create</span></span>

![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)

<span key="70989ed609584a548955f6108af1fa65"><span offset-key="70989ed609584a548955f6108af1fa65:0">When you create a new Hosted Zone in Route 53, AWS will assign a set of 4 name servers. You'll need to provide these name servers to your Engineering Manager so they can configure them in the domain registration record via our domain registrar.</span></span>

![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)

<span key="9a56eb4446a5477ca3aebfb53d81dbf7"><span offset-key="9a56eb4446a5477ca3aebfb53d81dbf7:0">You'll need to occasionally make modifications to your hosted zone records, you'll find those instructions embedded in these guides under specific services, such as Elastic Beanstalk.</span></span>

## 

<span key="2abccdd8836f465c91e9a80ff3d02aa8">**Product SSL Certificate**</span>

<span key="f3096288c24148dbb619626adde4607c"><span offset-key="f3096288c24148dbb619626adde4607c:0">Every internet-facing product should be protected using an SSL certificate. You'll use the AWS Certificate Manager to create this certificate, which can then be used with various services.</span></span>

1.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">1.</span>
    <span key="f6f438e01030495e89acfb6d9e8ae96a"><span offset-key="f6f438e01030495e89acfb6d9e8ae96a:0">Navigate to the Certificate Manager service</span></span>

2.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">2.</span>
    <span key="4e2d1eae548b4c6f9c7e62ba8ef97428"><span offset-key="4e2d1eae548b4c6f9c7e62ba8ef97428:0">'Request a Certificate'</span></span>

3.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">3.</span>
    <span key="f2535822395040dda950e56e36e0db17"><span offset-key="f2535822395040dda950e56e36e0db17:0">'Request a public certificate'</span></span>

4.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">4.</span>
    <span key="6dd13628b9af4198ad96a0edac868b98"><span offset-key="6dd13628b9af4198ad96a0edac868b98:0">Ensure these 4 names are listed on the certificate:</span></span>

    1.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">1.</span>
        <span key="98d86d062d77462c95d85e1b02847604"><span offset-key="98d86d062d77462c95d85e1b02847604:0">The root domain (e.g. </span>`ecosoap.dev`<span offset-key="98d86d062d77462c95d85e1b02847604:2">)</span></span>

    2.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">2.</span>
        <span key="b28a8c9eb372406ab431e152ed07cca2"><span offset-key="b28a8c9eb372406ab431e152ed07cca2:0">All first-level subdomains (e.g. </span>`*.ecosoap.dev`<span offset-key="b28a8c9eb372406ab431e152ed07cca2:2">)</span></span>

    3.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">3.</span>
        <span key="8373dbc2a4ac4dbeadd15aec7b382258"><span offset-key="8373dbc2a4ac4dbeadd15aec7b382258:0">All subdomains under </span>`api`<span offset-key="8373dbc2a4ac4dbeadd15aec7b382258:2"> (e.g. </span>`*.api.ecosoap.dev`<span offset-key="8373dbc2a4ac4dbeadd15aec7b382258:4">)</span></span>

    4.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">4.</span>
        <span key="338d0b06692e401e92334c464339930d"><span offset-key="338d0b06692e401e92334c464339930d:0">All subdomains under </span>`ds`<span offset-key="338d0b06692e401e92334c464339930d:2"> (e.g. </span>`*.ds.ecosoap.dev`<span offset-key="338d0b06692e401e92334c464339930d:4">)</span></span>

5.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">5.</span>
    <span key="a4cd48163b18402bab3ca25b28ac1b97"><span offset-key="a4cd48163b18402bab3ca25b28ac1b97:0">Click Next</span></span>

6.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">6.</span>
    <span key="465e534feb4d4f1897a3521c1bc1bcdd"><span offset-key="465e534feb4d4f1897a3521c1bc1bcdd:0">Choose 'DNS Validation'</span></span>

7.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">7.</span>
    <span key="89b35242730b40cb9190992247c019d0"><span offset-key="89b35242730b40cb9190992247c019d0:0">No tags are required</span></span>

8.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">8.</span>
    <span key="a26a0583f1f94d0ab171d1e8fbdac8ad"><span offset-key="a26a0583f1f94d0ab171d1e8fbdac8ad:0">Click 'Review' then 'Confirm and Request'</span></span>

9.  <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">9.</span>
    <span key="7b2194c34f4943f5a3ef1d2490564933"><span offset-key="7b2194c34f4943f5a3ef1d2490564933:0">For each of the names on the certificate, click the triangle and then click the button to add the entry to the hosted zone.</span></span>

10. <span class="r-1awozwy r-1nf4jbm r-6koalj r-18u37iz r-gg6oyi r-ubezar r-16dba41 r-135wba7 r-1m04atk r-1pyaxff" contenteditable="false" style="height:24px">10.</span>
    <span key="a73ec74bc0cb4a3c883107ee08dc13a3"><span offset-key="a73ec74bc0cb4a3c883107ee08dc13a3:0">After some time, around 10 minutes, the certificate should be fully validated and ready to use.</span></span>

![](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)

<span key="1bbd0da67ed34179822babef7de21844"><span offset-key="1bbd0da67ed34179822babef7de21844:0">You'll use this certificate as part of other services. You'll find those instructions embedded in these guides under specific services, such as Elastic Beanstalk.</span></span>
